{"tid":1489522,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"唔好睇小斬人案，佢會成為集中營理由","createTime":"2019-08-20T01:45:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-20T01:59:34.000Z","uid":242083,"like":21,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"25461ef23e6975784997927b16a0e4e5fc2c5c48","tid":1489522,"uid":242083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T01:45:38.000Z","msg":"喺中國發生斬人案後，中國鐵路都要檢查行李，放曬鐵馬俾人排隊，放個屋企，行下街都要俾人check袋<br />\n喺新疆西藏，更以消除危險為由，開始左集中營同高壓管理<br />\n即使喺大街，餐廳都有機會要檢查你行李。<br />\n十米可以就有警察站崗。<br />\n<br />\n香港唔係冇發生過斬人案，但呢次國家開始定性反送中係恐怖主義，咁斬人案極有機會被扣帽落恐怖主義度，嚟一次名正言順嘅監控制度。"},{"pid":"11eea9b10fa8da657733746d2f1d07f6c5b32273","tid":1489522,"uid":242083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T01:46:46.000Z","msg":"希望我諗多"},{"pid":"c6054608a48bfe191801bc9558f3e6a86effddf8","tid":1489522,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T01:47:21.000Z","msg":"係<br />\n唔好俾佢乘機侵食自由<br />\n啲狗信唔過"},{"pid":"f5a2c5d0a9177e7a817129dc021988161e5e8665","tid":1489522,"uid":89184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T01:47:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"33b9630b3446a800dcdc3432270f488107bc4a61","tid":1489522,"uid":231758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T01:48:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebb17599dabef60263ea959ccfe81cf7eda3d88b","tid":1489522,"uid":209248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T01:48:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"beaebcf4cf2bb16e767379b96e23c6cb24a12674","tid":1489522,"uid":299276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T01:48:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c73c8dae9bfe9292525ba72bf53eac75ade0e623","tid":1489522,"uid":133674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T01:49:18.000Z","msg":"細思極恐"},{"pid":"e0746a1fbadf5ad7452edf433a960d720e8256d7","tid":14895